title: Asia - Live in russia (progressive rock)
description:
A good progg concert with a great group! recorded at Olympski Stadium in Moscow, november 1990.

Line-up:
John Wetton - Lead voice, bass guitar, grand piano, accoustic guitar
Carl Palmer - Drums and percussion
Geoff Downes - Keyborads and harmony voclas
Pat Thrall - Guitar and harmony vocals.

Playlist:
1. Time Again
2. Sole Survivor
3. Don't Cry
4. Keyboard Solo
5. Only Time Will Tell
6. Rock and Roll Dream
7. Starless

9. The Smile Has Left Your Eyes
10. The Heat Goes On
11. Go
12. Heart Of The Moment
13. Open Your Eyes
14. Kari-Anne
